:::'''Glykon:''' ...Oh, maybe you haven't heard about me, but it's impossible that you haven't heard of me.
:::'''Glykon:''' I am Glykon of Okeanas. It is an ancient Amphorean city-state known for competitive sports.
:::'''Glykon:''' You may have heard that the people of Okeanas love to push the limits of their bodies, but you've probably never seen "the limit." Well, now you have. I am the limit.
:::'''Glykon:''' Hahaha, you don't think I'm tooting my own horn, do you? It's a shame that Okhema has yet to host any large-scale sports competition on the same level, so I don't blame you for not knowing me.
:::'''Glykon:''' But now that you do, you'll be worshiping me in no time. Bwahaha!
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} About the sports event you mentioned...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504063210-->
:::'''Glykon:''' The Okeanas Games &mdash; the most renowned sports event in the entire Amphoreus! Goodness, do I really need to explain it to you again? Amphoreus really is doomed.
:::'''Glykon:''' The Okeanas Games cover every kind of sports competition you can think of, including track and field, boxing, wrestling, gladiatorial combat, horse racing, and so on.
:::'''Glykon:''' Unlike the vicious and aggressive ways of the Kremnoans, we promote the immaculate spirit of competition in the Games &mdash; so please don't mix us up with those uncouth tribes.
:::'''Glykon:''' And you know what? Discus throw is the most eye-catching event of all! And yours truly is the three-peat discus throw champion!
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Absolute dominion!
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504063215-->
::::'''Glykon:''' That is why I am held as an esteemed guest at Dawncloud.
::::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504063218-->
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504063218-->
