::{{DIcon|Talk}} Has anyone ever called you... narcissistic?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504063220-->
:::'''Glykon:''' Bahaha! You can be frank about it. Yes, I am very narcissistic! So much that it annoys people.
:::'''Glykon:''' But what can I do? My overflowing charm rubs off on me too! Such is my burden.
:::'''Glykon:''' As someone from Okeanas, this narcissism is a part of my duty. The Okeanas spirit is to display my fit body and capture those who don't understand the spirit of competition with its excellence.
:::'''Glykon:''' Many have advised me to turn it down a notch, but I've never gotten in their faces about it, not at all! They are just jealous, and I am not obligated to take advice from charmless folk.
:::'''Glykon:''' Hahaha, what do you think? Do you want my autographed slate now?
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
